            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
           Speaker: &lt;a href=&quot;/scale9x/speakers/deb-nicholson&quot;&gt;Deb Nicholson&lt;/a&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;
