            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
           Speaker: &lt;a href=&quot;/scale9x/speakers/tom-king&quot;&gt;Tom King&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Speaker: &lt;a href=&quot;/scale9x/speakers/rick-boatright&quot;&gt;Rick Boatright&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;
